               <p>JOHN BAKER. I am a <rs id="t18180617-166-viclabel924" type="occupation">merchant's clerk</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18180617-166-victim1370 t18180617-166-viclabel924"></join>. On the 24th of May, at half-past nine o'clock at night, I was near St. Clement's Church, in the Strand, and felt something at my pocket. I immediately turned round, and saw the prisoner, Clark, give my hankerchief to Freeman. I secured both of them, and gave them in charge.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18180617-166-person1371">
                  WILLIAM 
                  BOND
               <interp inst="t18180617-166-person1371" type="surname" value="BOND"></interp>
