                  </persName>
            . I am an officer. I was coming along the Strand-Mr. Baker gave the prisoners into my charge.</p>
               <p>(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>CLARK'S Defence. I never touched it.</p>
               <p>FREEMAN's Defence. It was thrown into my hand.</p>
